:!cmd: execute the shell command
:r !cmd: execute the shell command, and insert the command output below the cursor
:w !cmd: send the current buffer as stdin to the shell command, and execute the command
:.!cmd: send the current line as stdin to the shell command, execute the command, and replace the current line with the command output
:%!cmd: send the entire buffer as stdin to the shell command, execute the command, and replace the entire buffer with the command output
:'<,'>!cmd: send the selection as stdin to the shell command, execute the command, and replace the selection with the command output
